CLP Hong Kong Sees Pressure to Raise Power Fees, RTHK Reports

-- B y   S o p h i e   L e u n g
-- 
2011-10-22T05:14:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-22/clp-hong-kong-sees-pressure-to-raise-power-fees-rthk-reports.html
CLP Power  Hong Kong  Ltd. sees
pressure to raise fees on rising global fuel prices and
inflation, Radio Television Hong Kong reported today, citing
Betty Yuen, vice chairman at the company.  The power company will talk to the city government about
reviewing electricity fees in the coming months, the Chinese-
language report cited Yuen as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sophie Leung in Hong Kong at 
 sleung59@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
